    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Even grasping the amber handle of this <em>+1 striking shock light mace</em> makes your hair stand on end.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> command, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The wielder of a <em>grounding spike</em> is within 30 feet</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A great surge of electricity connects your paired weapons. All creatures in a line between you and the wielder of the grounding spike take @Damage[4d12[electricity]] (@Check[type:reflex|dc:24|basic:true]).</p>\n<p><strong>Special</strong> The polarizing mace pairs with the <em>grounding spike</em>.</p>"
